cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with wireless communication networks and their optimization, which falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), cognitive radio (cs.CR), system and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper specifically focuses on cognitive wireless powered network (WPCN) and spectrum sharing models, which are relevant to all of these sub-categories.
